1. On često* putuje po svetu. (He often travels around the world.)
2. Ona često* plače. (She often cries.)
3. Oni često* idu u grad. (They often go to town.)
4. Mi često* igramo fudbal. (We often play football.)
5. Oni često* jutrom idu u šetnju. (They often go for a walk in the morning.)
6. Mi često* razgovaramo o raznim temama. (We often talk about various topics.)